freetext.SYMPTOMS_DESCRIPTION: General tiredness, slight headache, poor appetite, delayed pain in arm at injection site, kind of like low grade flu symptoms but not awful.

freetext.SYSTEMIC_REACTION_OTHER: Complicated because i also have pneumotitis. Pain at injection site for dose 1 came back with a vengence and just today has begun to resolve.
Complicated by significant case of pneumotitis
